              "file": "bench-artifacts/cache-api.md",
              "patch": "Index: bench-artifacts/cache-api.md\n===================================================================\n--- bench-artifacts/cache-api.md\t\n+++ bench-artifacts/cache-api.md\t\n@@ -0,0 +1,49 @@\n+# Cache API\n+\n+## createCache()\n+\n+Creates a new cache instance with a Map-based storage structure.\n+\n+```javascript\n+import { createCache } from './cache.mjs'\n+\n+const cache = createCache()\n+```\n+\n+Returns an object containing the following methods:\n+\n+## Methods\n+\n+### get(key)\n+\n+Retrieves a value from the cache by key.\n+\n+- **Parameter:**\n+  - `key` - The cache key to look up\n+  \n+- **Returns:** The cached value if found, otherwise `undefined`\n+\n+### set(key, value)\n+\n+Sets the given value in the cache.\n+\n+- **Parameters:**\n+  - `key` - The cache key\n+  - `value` - The value to cache\n+  \n+- **Returns:** The value that was set\n+\n+### delete(key)\n+\n+Removes a value from the cache.\n+\n+- **Parameter:**\n+  - `key` - The cache key to remove\n+  \n+- **Returns:** `true` if the key existed and was removed, `false` otherwise\n+\n+### clear()\n+\n+Removes all entries from the cache.\n+\n+- **Returns:** `undefined`\n",
              "additions": 49,
